<%#
# Attachment Form Partial

This partial renders an input element for attached file.
By default, the input is a input with the `type="file"` attribute.

## Local variables:

- `f`:
  A Rails form generator, used to help create the appropriate input fields.
- `field`:
  An instance of [Administrate::Field::Attachment][1].
  A wrapper around the Attachment pulled from the model.

%>

<div class="field-unit__label">
  <%= f.label field.attribute %>
</div>
<div class="field-unit__field">
  <%= f.file_field field.attribute %>
</div>
